name: Julah Myriah
description: Life is all bright and colorful. Therefore, I love all that is connected with an active way of life. But life will appear for me a fairy tale when I meet You! In a life I’m an optimist and like making my life fun. Everyday I try to make myself, my relatives and friends special, romantic and bright. You Wish to try?. Trust me, I am romantic, tender, honest, intelligent and active lady. They say the strength of a woman is in her weakness. I absolutely agree. My dream is to be in arms of right and wise man. I am romantic may be that is why I enjoy spending my time on the beach, looking at the stars, feeling fresh breeze from the sea.
